HEADWORD: Shotgun
<hw>Shot"gun`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A light,
smooth-bored gun, often double-barreled, especially designed for firing
small shot at short range, and killing small game.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shot-proof</ent>⟦br⟧
